Title: Jump the Shark
Plot: The agents ask the Lone Gunmen to help find their friendly foe Yves Adele Harlow after former Area 51 Man-In-Black Morris Fletcher claims she is one of the super-soldiers.
Writer: Vince Gilligan, John Shiban, Frank Spotnitz
GuestStars: Michael McKean, Stephen Snedden, Zuleikha Robinson, Jim Fyfe, Marcus Giamatti, Pamela Paulshock, Michael Edward Thomas, Robert Joseph, Thomas Schnauz, John Prosky, Timothy Landfield
